# Keep the Docker build context small and free of secrets / build artifacts.
# The build needs: root manifests + lockfile + pnpm-workspace.yaml, apps/web,
# bridge, packages/shared source. Everything below is excluded.

# Dependencies & build output (reinstalled / rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.turbo

# VCS & CI artifacts
.git
.github
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
playwright-report
test-results

# Secrets & local env (NEVER copy real env into an image)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
.env.docker

# Logs & local runner state
**/*.log
docs/production-hardening/runner.log
docs/production-hardening/STATUS.md
docs/production-hardening/DONE.flag

# Local/dev-only tooling not needed in the image
.devcontainer
.worktrees
graphify-out
supabase/.temp
*.lnk
agentroom_graph_*.html
